#
#  Synopsis:
#	How to install blobio.
#  Note:
#	This document desparatley needs improvement.
#	Desparatley.
#

BlobIO has been built and tested on MacOS/Darwin back to Snow Leopard
(10.6, 64bi) and Linux back to 64bit 2.32.


On 64 bit Linux systems, do

	cp local-linux.mk.example local.mk

	#  tweak for your environment
	vi local.mk
	make world		#  default target is /usr/local/blobio

On modern Mac/Darwin, do

	cp local-linux.mk.example local.mk

	#  tweak local.mk for your environment
	vi local-darwin.mk.example local.mk

	make world		#  default target is /usr/local/blobio
